1
00:01:41,250 --> 00:01:45,500
[XIANG] And so after
all of that, what happened?

2
00:01:45,583 --> 00:01:48,541
[ZHENG] I was put onto the
marketeers' horse cart.

3
00:01:48,625 --> 00:01:52,833
But I have few memories
of what happened around then.

4
00:01:52,916 --> 00:01:54,291
I dreamt.

5
00:01:54,375 --> 00:01:55,750
[gasps]

6
00:01:57,125 --> 00:02:00,791
Horrible dreams
I never had before.

7
00:02:02,541 --> 00:02:10,500
[wind blows, grass rustling]

8
00:02:13,791 --> 00:02:15,625
[ZHENG] Huh?

9
00:02:24,041 --> 00:02:26,000
[HALLUCINATION laughing]

10
00:02:26,083 --> 00:02:31,916
--[ZHENG gasping]
--[HALLUCINATION laughing]

11
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:35,166
[ZHENG]
Huh? Huh?!

12
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:38,541
[HALLUCINATION]
Who's gonna be the king now?

13
00:02:40,458 --> 00:02:42,583
--[ZHENG] Uuuh!
--[HALLUCINATION laughing]

14
00:02:42,666 --> 00:02:43,791
[ZHENG] Eeh!

15
00:02:43,875 --> 00:02:47,416
[HALLUCINATION]
Who's gonna be the king?

16
00:02:47,500 --> 00:02:49,000
Who is it?

17
00:02:49,083 --> 00:02:50,583
[yells]

18
00:02:50,666 --> 00:02:52,333
[horses neigh]

19
00:02:59,708 --> 00:03:02,958
You're awake now finally.

20
00:03:03,041 --> 00:03:04,791
Is it you?

21
00:03:06,291 --> 00:03:07,541
[ZI XIA] Hm.

22
00:03:07,625 --> 00:03:09,583
[gasps]

23
00:03:11,875 --> 00:03:13,416
[ZHENG] Uuuh...

24
00:03:14,833 --> 00:03:18,833
[yells, screams]

25
00:03:24,916 --> 00:03:26,541
--[DAO JIAN] What's wrong?
--[ZHENG screaming]

26
00:03:26,625 --> 00:03:30,583
Please! Please,
calm yourself, my lord!

27
00:03:30,666 --> 00:03:32,208
You must be frightened
to wake up

28
00:03:32,291 --> 00:03:34,541
and find yourself
on a horse cart.

29
00:03:34,625 --> 00:03:37,416
But I-I can explain.
Please, let me explain!

30
00:03:37,500 --> 00:03:39,875
Calm yourself
my lord, please!

31
00:03:42,541 --> 00:03:44,500
[DAO JIAN]
And that's where we stand.

32
00:03:44,583 --> 00:03:46,500
We are currently plotting
your mother's return

33
00:03:46,583 --> 00:03:47,791
by a different route.

34
00:03:47,875 --> 00:03:49,041
Do not worry.

35
00:03:49,125 --> 00:03:52,208
You will surely be
reunited in Xianyang.

36
00:03:52,291 --> 00:03:54,875
We still have a way
to go before the gate.

37
00:03:54,958 --> 00:03:57,583
Why don't you just rest
for a little while longer.

38
00:03:57,666 --> 00:03:59,041
[DAO JIAN]
Hm.

39
00:03:59,125 --> 00:04:01,791
And you can reach the gate
for sure like this, then?

40
00:04:01,875 --> 00:04:03,541
[ZI XIA]
It's the best way.

41
00:04:03,625 --> 00:04:06,875
We're taking our usual road
to avoid arousing suspicion.

42
00:04:06,958 --> 00:04:09,583
This road will pass through
five different gates

43
00:04:09,666 --> 00:04:11,458
on our way out of Zhao.

44
00:04:11,541 --> 00:04:14,333
Once we're past those,
we'll be cleared for Qin.

45
00:04:14,416 --> 00:04:17,083
Hmmm. Five you say?

46
00:04:17,166 --> 00:04:19,375
We--we were prepared for this,

47
00:04:19,458 --> 00:04:21,291
but you do have
a way to get us past

48
00:04:21,375 --> 00:04:22,833
the inspectors, am I right?

49
00:04:22,916 --> 00:04:25,083
Oh come on now.
Just leave that to us.

50
00:04:25,166 --> 00:04:27,500
We're not amateurs.

51
00:04:27,583 --> 00:04:29,958
So there're five gates
till Qin from now.

52
00:04:30,041 --> 00:04:32,291
[ZI XIA]
No need to worry at all.

53
00:04:32,375 --> 00:04:34,333
Trust me, Zi Xia
will get you to Qin

54
00:04:34,416 --> 00:04:36,916
safe and sound. You will see.

55
00:04:41,458 --> 00:04:43,041
Hm?

56
00:04:44,250 --> 00:04:46,750
Is this real? At all?

57
00:04:46,833 --> 00:04:49,000
[ZI XIA]
Of course it is real.

58
00:04:52,958 --> 00:04:57,333
[ZHAO SOLDIERS,
MERCHANTS chatter]

59
00:04:57,416 --> 00:05:05,291
--[eerie music plays]
--[chattering continues]

60
00:05:05,375 --> 00:05:09,166
[eerie music continues]

61
00:05:09,250 --> 00:05:11,250
[TIAN CI grunts]

62
00:05:11,333 --> 00:05:15,916
[DAO JIAN gasps,
DAN YUAN grunts]

63
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:17,583
All right, here we go!

64
00:05:17,666 --> 00:05:19,166
There is an empty rice bundle.

65
00:05:19,250 --> 00:05:22,041
Lord Zheng, you go in there.

66
00:05:22,125 --> 00:05:23,708
I will take
the reins from now on,

67
00:05:23,791 --> 00:05:25,708
just follow my lead.

68
00:05:25,791 --> 00:05:28,083
[CIVIL SERVANT 208A]
Next! And hurry it up!

69
00:05:28,166 --> 00:05:29,750
C'mon! Next!

70
00:05:29,833 --> 00:05:31,583
What kind of cargo is this?

71
00:05:31,666 --> 00:05:33,333
Aren't these gold coins?

72
00:05:33,416 --> 00:05:34,583
Grab him right now!

73
00:05:34,666 --> 00:05:35,791
Huh? No!

74
00:05:35,875 --> 00:05:39,750
It's not--please, don't! No!

75
00:05:39,833 --> 00:05:43,916
[whimpers]

76
00:05:46,125 --> 00:05:48,416
[CIVIL SERVANT 208A]
All right, next!

77
00:06:01,083 --> 00:06:02,250
[CIVIL SERVANT 208A grunts]

78
00:06:02,333 --> 00:06:03,375
[ZI XIA]
Thanks again!

79
00:06:03,458 --> 00:06:06,083
Yep! Go on through now!

80
00:06:11,333 --> 00:06:14,416
[CIVIL SERVANT 208A]
Okay, next!

81
00:06:17,958 --> 00:06:19,458
[DAO JIAN] Hmmm.

82
00:06:24,541 --> 00:06:26,250
Wh-What was all that?

83
00:06:26,333 --> 00:06:28,333
That's all it takes
to pass a gate?

84
00:06:28,416 --> 00:06:30,625
Us black marketeers
deal in illegal goods,

85
00:06:30,708 --> 00:06:32,083
you understand me?

86
00:06:32,166 --> 00:06:35,541
We must always, always be
prepared for everything.

87
00:06:35,625 --> 00:06:36,916
[TIAN CI, DAN YUAN sigh]

88
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,708
[YA MEN]
Don't get the wrong idea.

89
00:06:38,791 --> 00:06:40,666
Not all black marketeers
can slip through

90
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,291
just like that, like us.

91
00:06:42,375 --> 00:06:44,583
She can because she's Zi Xia.

92
00:06:44,666 --> 00:06:47,291
After she took over,
our business grew to easily

93
00:06:47,375 --> 00:06:50,166
twice the size
as it was before.

94
00:06:51,250 --> 00:06:52,625
[laughs]

95
00:06:52,708 --> 00:06:55,125
Just good business sense!

96
00:06:55,208 --> 00:06:57,250
[DAO JIAN] Lü Buwei
recommended these youngsters

97
00:06:57,333 --> 00:07:00,375
so fiercely.
Actually, I had my doubts,

98
00:07:00,458 --> 00:07:03,375
but now, I understand.

99
00:07:14,166 --> 00:07:15,916
[ZI XIA] Now that I
get a good look at him,

100
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:18,250
he's just a mess of bruises.

101
00:07:18,333 --> 00:07:20,625
It must be a daily thing.

102
00:07:20,708 --> 00:07:23,333
[ZHENG breathes shakily]

103
00:07:23,416 --> 00:07:25,041
[ZI XIA]
Lord Zheng?

104
00:07:25,125 --> 00:07:28,291
[ZHENG breathes shakily]

105
00:07:29,125 --> 00:07:34,041
[GHOSTS] Can't breathe.
Can't breathe. The pain.

106
00:07:34,125 --> 00:07:39,625
Can't breathe.
Can't breathe. The pain.

107
00:07:39,708 --> 00:07:44,458
Can't breathe.
Can't breathe. Can't breathe.

108
00:07:44,541 --> 00:07:48,666
[GHOST 208A] Don't go.
We won't let you, Zheng.

109
00:07:48,750 --> 00:07:50,333
Can't breathe.

110
00:07:50,416 --> 00:07:53,000
[GHOST 208C]
As if we'd let you go.

111
00:07:53,083 --> 00:07:55,416
[GHOST 208D]
To the depths of the earth.

112
00:07:55,500 --> 00:07:56,875
The depths of the earth.

113
00:07:56,958 --> 00:07:59,583
[ZHENG] Shut up! I had
nothing to do with Changping!

114
00:07:59,666 --> 00:08:01,625
I'm going back to Qin!

115
00:08:01,708 --> 00:08:05,416
[HALLUCINATION]
Doing what? To Qin?

116
00:08:05,500 --> 00:08:08,208
Who is? Who is?

117
00:08:08,291 --> 00:08:10,625
Doing what? Going back?

118
00:08:10,708 --> 00:08:13,708
Back to Qin and then what?

119
00:08:13,791 --> 00:08:16,416
[laughs intensely]

120
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:19,041
You're kidding, right?

121
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:25,000
[HALLUCINATION]
After all, you're already--

122
00:08:25,083 --> 00:08:27,500
[ZHENG screaming]

123
00:08:27,583 --> 00:08:28,541
[DAO JIAN]
What happened?

124
00:08:28,625 --> 00:08:30,166
[YA MEN]
Not again!

125
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:32,500
--[ZHENG panting]
--[ZI XIA] Lord Zheng!

126
00:08:32,583 --> 00:08:35,833
[panting]

127
00:08:37,958 --> 00:08:40,625
[DAO JIAN] So Lord Zheng
is acting strange?

128
00:08:40,708 --> 00:08:41,750
[ZI XIA] Mm.

129
00:08:41,833 --> 00:08:44,041
But anyone can be
tormented by dreams.

130
00:08:44,125 --> 00:08:45,250
It's normal.

131
00:08:45,333 --> 00:08:47,083
He's likely
still a bit confused

132
00:08:47,166 --> 00:08:50,291
by his sudden change
in circumstances.

133
00:08:50,375 --> 00:08:51,750
But maybe--

134
00:08:51,833 --> 00:08:55,166
Regardless, we must first
of all escape Zhao safely.

135
00:08:55,250 --> 00:08:57,708
And only that, Zi Xia.

136
00:08:57,791 --> 00:08:59,291
[ZI XIA sighs]

137
00:09:00,291 --> 00:09:01,333
[DAO JIAN]
Another gate.

138
00:09:01,416 --> 00:09:03,666
Into the bundle, Lord Zheng.

139
00:09:08,958 --> 00:09:12,583
[ZI XIA] So getting out
of Zhao comes first, hm?

140
00:09:12,666 --> 00:09:14,041
That's true, but--

141
00:09:14,125 --> 00:09:16,666
[horses neigh]

142
00:09:16,750 --> 00:09:19,250
[ZHAO SOLDIERS murmur]

143
00:09:19,333 --> 00:09:20,291
[chuckles]

144
00:09:20,375 --> 00:09:21,750
Hey, that's nice!

145
00:09:21,833 --> 00:09:22,958
My shift's finally
over in about...

146
00:09:23,041 --> 00:09:25,125
[MAO YING]
Oh, Zi Xia! Zi Xia!

147
00:09:25,208 --> 00:09:26,708
It's been so long!

148
00:09:26,791 --> 00:09:29,083
You look so well,
dear Mao Ying.

149
00:09:29,166 --> 00:09:31,000
I haven't seen you
around here lately.

150
00:09:31,083 --> 00:09:33,958
You weren't possibly avoiding
me now, were you, my dear?

151
00:09:34,041 --> 00:09:35,916
I would never do that!

152
00:09:36,000 --> 00:09:38,416
[laughs] Why don't you
rest here a while?

153
00:09:38,500 --> 00:09:39,833
I'll get you some tea.

154
00:09:39,916 --> 00:09:42,791
[ZI XIA] I'd love to,
but we're in a bit of a hurry.

155
00:09:42,875 --> 00:09:45,208
Too bad! Spend some time
with me for once!

156
00:09:45,291 --> 00:09:47,250
Or I will just order
a cargo inspection

157
00:09:47,333 --> 00:09:49,750
and make you stay here
against your will!

158
00:09:49,833 --> 00:09:52,541
[ZI XIA] I certainly
wouldn't want you to do that.

159
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:54,333
But there are so many
customers of mine

160
00:09:54,416 --> 00:09:57,083
waiting for their goods, so
let's have that tea another--

161
00:09:57,166 --> 00:09:58,541
[gasps]

162
00:10:00,958 --> 00:10:02,916
[BOTH gasp]

163
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,375
--[ZI XIA] Hey!
--[ZHAO SOLDIER 208D] Uh.

164
00:10:04,458 --> 00:10:07,458
[MAO YING] Hey! Wh-What do
you think you're doing?

165
00:10:07,541 --> 00:10:09,791
[ZHAO SOLDIER 208D]
Me? Doing some test shots!

166
00:10:09,875 --> 00:10:12,833
Bought this bow yesterday and
thought I'd try it out now.

167
00:10:12,916 --> 00:10:14,625
[ZI XIA] Cut that out.
It's not a joke!

168
00:10:14,708 --> 00:10:15,958
Don't be angry, Zi Xia!

169
00:10:16,041 --> 00:10:17,250
The thing is,
this guy's brand-new,

170
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:19,333
and he doesn't know
the protocol!

171
00:10:19,416 --> 00:10:20,416
[ZI XIA grunts]

172
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,625
[MAO YING] Uh-guh-guh!
G-Go on, now.

173
00:10:22,708 --> 00:10:24,083
[ZI XIA]
Mm.

174
00:10:26,666 --> 00:10:28,291
[ZI XIA]
Blood?

175
00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:37,333
[ZI XIA] I haven't heard
any screams or whimpers

176
00:10:37,416 --> 00:10:39,833
ever since we left the gate.

177
00:10:39,916 --> 00:10:42,958
Has he passed out?
Or is he--

178
00:10:48,416 --> 00:10:50,208
Lord Zheng!

179
00:10:52,125 --> 00:10:54,500
Pull it out. I can't.

180
00:10:54,583 --> 00:10:56,458
Ugh!

181
00:10:56,541 --> 00:10:58,750
My lord Zheng!
You are all right

182
00:10:58,833 --> 00:11:01,791
and you endured that without
even uttering a single word!

183
00:11:01,875 --> 00:11:03,333
[ZI XIA]
Hang on.

184
00:11:03,416 --> 00:11:06,916
What child wouldn't cry
as an arrow pierces his arm?

185
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,333
H-H-Here I go.

186
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:16,458
[ZI XIA] What human
wouldn't even blink an eye

187
00:11:16,541 --> 00:11:19,166
as that arrow is
pulled from his arm?

188
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:21,916
What's with this child?

189
00:11:25,875 --> 00:11:28,333
[ZI XIA] Hardship in your
younger years really can

190
00:11:28,416 --> 00:11:31,333
suppress your emotions.

191
00:11:31,416 --> 00:11:33,708
We war orphans were the same

192
00:11:33,791 --> 00:11:36,708
until our adopted
father took us in.

193
00:11:36,791 --> 00:11:40,125
But, to not budge
after taking an arrow?

194
00:11:40,208 --> 00:11:42,791
That goes beyond
mere emotions, I'd say.

195
00:11:42,875 --> 00:11:45,458
The boy is clearly not normal.

196
00:11:45,541 --> 00:11:47,333
Something's definitely going on,

197
00:11:47,416 --> 00:11:49,750
in his body and mind.

198
00:11:57,416 --> 00:12:00,916
[NARRATOR] Four days after
Zi Xia and crew left Handan,

199
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:04,958
at last they arrived at the
fifth and final gate, Lü Gan.

200
00:12:05,041 --> 00:12:06,250
Once past Lü Gan,

201
00:12:06,333 --> 00:12:08,208
it was a half-day's
distance to the border

202
00:12:08,291 --> 00:12:10,250
between Qin and Zhao.

203
00:12:11,916 --> 00:12:14,250
[ZI XIA]
Is something wrong?

204
00:12:14,333 --> 00:12:17,458
The moon's out once again.

205
00:12:17,541 --> 00:12:20,291
True, that it is.

206
00:12:20,375 --> 00:12:21,458
I like your eyes when you're

207
00:12:21,541 --> 00:12:23,750
looking at the moon,
Lord Zheng.

208
00:12:25,375 --> 00:12:29,500
[ZHENG] Sometimes I can't
tell dream from reality.

209
00:12:29,583 --> 00:12:32,708
That must be
really difficult for you.

210
00:12:32,791 --> 00:12:35,083
Just remember that
when I'm right here,

211
00:12:35,166 --> 00:12:37,458
it's all very real.

212
00:12:37,541 --> 00:12:40,291
--[ZHENG] Zi Xia.
--[ZI XIA] Huh?

213
00:12:40,375 --> 00:12:44,375
Do you really think I'll
be able to go back to Qin?

214
00:12:46,166 --> 00:12:48,541
It's like I said before,

215
00:12:48,625 --> 00:12:51,500
I'm taking you back. Period.

216
00:12:54,416 --> 00:12:56,000
[CIVIL SERVANTS,
ZHAO SOLDIERS chatter]

217
00:12:56,083 --> 00:12:58,041
[CIVIL SERVANT 208B]
You may pass!

218
00:13:00,916 --> 00:13:03,708
Hang on there, now!

219
00:13:03,791 --> 00:13:04,916
[DAO JIAN]
Huh?

220
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,708
[CIVIL SERVANT 208C]
What's going on, Zi Xia?

221
00:13:06,791 --> 00:13:08,958
I don't recognize
half these people!

222
00:13:09,041 --> 00:13:11,583
Who are they, huh?

223
00:13:11,666 --> 00:13:13,083
We were short a few,

224
00:13:13,166 --> 00:13:15,875
so I just hired them
in a village.

225
00:13:15,958 --> 00:13:18,083
Oh well, they may be older

226
00:13:18,166 --> 00:13:19,750
but they're of no use to me!

227
00:13:19,833 --> 00:13:22,708
In fact they're just
weighing me down.

228
00:13:22,791 --> 00:13:24,375
I'll just leave them here,

229
00:13:24,458 --> 00:13:27,416
and you can put them
on the next cart out.

230
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:29,875
Aah. Ugh!

231
00:13:29,958 --> 00:13:34,416
Oh fine, fine! Get outta
the way! Goodbye!

232
00:13:37,166 --> 00:13:38,833
[DAN YUAN huffs]

233
00:13:38,916 --> 00:13:42,083
That... was... a close one!

234
00:13:42,166 --> 00:13:43,166
Uuh!

235
00:13:43,250 --> 00:13:44,500
[ZHAO SOLDIER 208F]
A smoke signal!

236
00:13:44,583 --> 00:13:46,791
It's the signal for
an emergency lockdown!

237
00:13:46,875 --> 00:13:48,500
Close the gate!

238
00:13:48,583 --> 00:13:50,291
Close the gate!

239
00:13:52,416 --> 00:13:54,708
[TIAN CI gasps]
The gate's been shut!

240
00:13:54,791 --> 00:13:56,791
Have they found out
about Lord Zheng?

241
00:13:56,875 --> 00:13:59,291
M-Made it by a hair.

242
00:13:59,375 --> 00:14:00,583
[laughs]

243
00:14:00,666 --> 00:14:02,791
We did it! We made it in time!

244
00:14:02,875 --> 00:14:04,916
Past all, every single gate!

245
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:06,916
Now we can finally
get back to Qin!

246
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:08,125
[laughs]

247
00:14:08,208 --> 00:14:10,541
[JIANG ZHANG] This is no
time for rejoicing!

248
00:14:10,625 --> 00:14:12,375
If they were to
find out about Zheng,

249
00:14:12,458 --> 00:14:14,458
they will be after us all!

250
00:14:14,541 --> 00:14:16,458
With their whole army!

251
00:14:16,541 --> 00:14:17,958
They're quite right.

252
00:14:18,041 --> 00:14:20,333
No need for
disguises right now.

253
00:14:20,416 --> 00:14:22,541
We'll find a place
to dump our cargo,

254
00:14:22,625 --> 00:14:24,541
then it's full speed ahead!

255
00:14:24,625 --> 00:14:27,375
The Zhao cavalry
is fast, gentlemen!

256
00:14:31,458 --> 00:14:33,458
[DAO JIAN] Our rendezvous
point is just ahead.

257
00:14:33,541 --> 00:14:36,333
There should already be
troops there waiting for us.

258
00:14:36,416 --> 00:14:38,166
No signs that
we're being followed.

259
00:14:38,250 --> 00:14:40,375
We can go through!

260
00:14:40,458 --> 00:14:42,916
Zi Xia, you really
did save us all.

261
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,791
Things would never
have gone this smoothly

262
00:14:44,875 --> 00:14:47,541
without your help.
We thank you!

263
00:14:47,625 --> 00:14:49,833
[ZI XIA]
Saved you all?

264
00:14:51,333 --> 00:14:54,750
[ZI XIA] But have I truly
saved this poor child?

265
00:14:55,458 --> 00:14:57,583
[sighs]

266
00:14:57,666 --> 00:15:00,416
I promise you'll be
home soon, Lord Zheng.

267
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:02,833
Just think, once you
become the king,

268
00:15:02,916 --> 00:15:06,208
you'll be in the lap
of pure and genuine luxury!

269
00:15:06,291 --> 00:15:08,750
If I were ten years
younger or so,

270
00:15:08,833 --> 00:15:11,250
I could maybe even
be your wife.

271
00:15:11,333 --> 00:15:14,291
Aah! Living the
high life with you!

272
00:15:14,375 --> 00:15:15,875
Maybe "wife"'s too much.

273
00:15:15,958 --> 00:15:18,125
Concubine? Or servant?

274
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:19,916
[giggles]

275
00:15:21,625 --> 00:15:24,125
[ZI XIA] Lord Zheng?
Are you all right?

276
00:15:24,208 --> 00:15:26,500
Lord Zheng? Lord Zheng?

277
00:15:26,583 --> 00:15:28,458
--[HALLUCINATION] Wait.
--[ZHENG gasps]

278
00:15:31,583 --> 00:15:35,583
[HALLUCINATION]
Just. Hang on.

279
00:15:35,666 --> 00:15:39,125
Zheng. Zheng.

280
00:15:39,208 --> 00:15:41,458
Who's gonna be the king now?

281
00:15:41,541 --> 00:15:44,333
Who's gonna be the king?

282
00:15:44,416 --> 00:15:46,291
Who is it?

283
00:15:46,375 --> 00:15:50,291
Zheng. Zheng. Zheng.

284
00:15:50,375 --> 00:15:51,541
[ZHENG gasping]

285
00:15:51,625 --> 00:15:54,708
[HALLUCINATION]
Going back to Qin to be king?

286
00:15:54,791 --> 00:15:56,958
You must be dreaming.

287
00:15:57,041 --> 00:15:58,541
[laughs]

288
00:15:58,625 --> 00:16:01,875
Enough of this nonsense,
get off the cart.

289
00:16:01,958 --> 00:16:04,583
You can't possibly go to Qin.

290
00:16:04,666 --> 00:16:05,666
Shut up now!

291
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,916
Lord Zheng?
What's the matter?

292
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,500
Lord Zheng!

293
00:16:09,583 --> 00:16:11,291
[HALLUCINATION]
Who exactly will celebrate

294
00:16:11,375 --> 00:16:13,208
your homecoming?

295
00:16:13,291 --> 00:16:15,875
Who will? Your father?

296
00:16:15,958 --> 00:16:17,333
Don't make me laugh.

297
00:16:17,416 --> 00:16:19,250
He tossed you aside
seven years ago

298
00:16:19,333 --> 00:16:21,833
when he came back to Qin,
am I correct?

299
00:16:21,916 --> 00:16:24,500
Even your own mother
has shunned you as well.

300
00:16:24,583 --> 00:16:26,833
If it weren't for you,
then she could have

301
00:16:26,916 --> 00:16:29,250
gone back to being
a lady of Zhao!

302
00:16:29,333 --> 00:16:31,208
If it weren't for you.

303
00:16:31,291 --> 00:16:33,041
Stop! Stop it! Stop!

304
00:16:33,125 --> 00:16:35,625
[ZI XIA] Zheng!
What's wrong Lord Zheng?

305
00:16:35,708 --> 00:16:37,166
[HALLUCINATION laughs]

306
00:16:37,250 --> 00:16:40,333
Discarded by your father
and shunned by your mother.

307
00:16:40,416 --> 00:16:42,000
If you go back now
you'll only be

308
00:16:42,083 --> 00:16:43,833
a nuisance to them all.

309
00:16:43,916 --> 00:16:47,291
There's no real place for you
in Qin and you know it.

310
00:16:47,375 --> 00:16:50,500
But the biggest problem
still is always you.

311
00:16:50,583 --> 00:16:53,416
Your mind and
your body are so bizarre.

312
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:56,541
He-heh. A normal person
isn't so blasé

313
00:16:56,625 --> 00:17:00,875
when he's shot with an arrow--
a sane person, that is!

314
00:17:00,958 --> 00:17:04,250
You're smart so you
must have realized long ago,

315
00:17:04,333 --> 00:17:08,541
someone like you could
never ever actually be king!

316
00:17:08,625 --> 00:17:11,708
So, how long are you
going to stay on that cart?

317
00:17:11,791 --> 00:17:13,166
Get down off there now!

318
00:17:13,250 --> 00:17:16,708
[ZHENG yelling]

319
00:17:17,791 --> 00:17:18,833
[JIANG ZHANG]
Zheng's fallen off!

320
00:17:18,916 --> 00:17:20,750
--[TIAN CI] What?
--[DAO JIAN] Stop!

321
00:17:21,416 --> 00:17:23,000
[BOTH whinny]

322
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:24,041
[ZI XIA]
I'll get him!

323
00:17:24,125 --> 00:17:25,791
Everyone else wait there!

324
00:17:25,875 --> 00:17:27,208
[YA MEN]
Zi Xia!

325
00:17:27,291 --> 00:17:29,208
Man. What is really going on?

326
00:17:29,291 --> 00:17:30,583
[JIANG ZHANG]
Like I know?

327
00:17:30,666 --> 00:17:31,625
That little brat.

328
00:17:31,708 --> 00:17:33,666
We are running out
of time here!

329
00:17:35,500 --> 00:17:36,583
[ZI XIA]
Lord Zheng!

330
00:17:36,666 --> 00:17:39,291
[ZHENG]
Stay back!

331
00:17:39,375 --> 00:17:42,291
I... I can't go back to Qin.

332
00:17:42,375 --> 00:17:45,708
What do you mean?
But you'll be there so soon.

333
00:17:45,791 --> 00:17:48,125
[ZHENG] I can't.
There's a reason!

334
00:17:51,416 --> 00:17:52,291
[ZHENG gasps]

335
00:17:52,375 --> 00:17:53,791
--[squelch]
--[ZI XIA] Aah!

336
00:17:53,875 --> 00:17:55,291
What are you doing?

337
00:17:55,375 --> 00:17:59,458
Are you in your right mind?

338
00:17:59,541 --> 00:18:01,500
There's no pain at all!

339
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:05,083
Huh?

340
00:18:05,166 --> 00:18:06,791
And it is
not just the pain.

341
00:18:06,875 --> 00:18:08,583
It's the flavors. The smells.

342
00:18:08,666 --> 00:18:11,666
The heat, and even the cold.

343
00:18:11,750 --> 00:18:14,916
I feel nothing,
nothing at all.

344
00:18:15,000 --> 00:18:16,666
I don't understand.

345
00:18:16,750 --> 00:18:18,333
That just can't be true.

346
00:18:18,416 --> 00:18:20,375
[ZHENG] Uh!
Someone like that

347
00:18:20,458 --> 00:18:22,375
could never be king.

348
00:18:24,458 --> 00:18:27,833
But how can this be?

349
00:18:27,916 --> 00:18:32,125
Ever since I can remember,
I knew I was royalty,

350
00:18:32,208 --> 00:18:35,625
and my heart trembled
with the sheer honor of it.

351
00:18:35,708 --> 00:18:38,750
But one step outside,
and I was in the middle

352
00:18:38,833 --> 00:18:40,833
of a hostile land.

353
00:18:40,916 --> 00:18:43,666
Worse, the land whose
400 thousand soldiers

354
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:46,791
Qin had slaughtered
at Changping.

355
00:18:49,041 --> 00:18:51,125
[ZHENG]
The animosity toward Qin

356
00:18:51,208 --> 00:18:54,166
rained down upon me
without mercy.

357
00:18:54,250 --> 00:18:57,208
While enduring that
overwhelming violence,

358
00:18:57,291 --> 00:19:01,125
I saw the situation in which
I had been placed at birth,

359
00:19:01,208 --> 00:19:02,875
and despaired.

360
00:19:02,958 --> 00:19:05,208
As the days of
abuse continued,

361
00:19:05,291 --> 00:19:07,250
my heart closed more tightly,

362
00:19:07,333 --> 00:19:11,250
until eventually,
I could feel nothing at all.

363
00:19:14,375 --> 00:19:16,291
[ZI XIA]
How awful.

364
00:19:16,375 --> 00:19:20,416
To think, he was driven
to such intense extremes.

365
00:19:20,500 --> 00:19:22,166
And to think...

366
00:19:22,250 --> 00:19:24,958
...this child,
this prince of Qin,

367
00:19:25,041 --> 00:19:26,541
was born in Zhao.

368
00:19:26,625 --> 00:19:32,416
Because of that ill fortune
wholly beyond his control...

369
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:34,250
...he was made to
bear the brunt of

370
00:19:34,333 --> 00:19:36,250
their Changping grudge.

371
00:19:36,333 --> 00:19:38,583
A child not yet ten,
to whom no one

372
00:19:38,666 --> 00:19:41,750
held out a helping hand,
left all alone.

373
00:19:41,833 --> 00:19:43,833
This whole time.

374
00:19:45,625 --> 00:19:48,000
--[ZI XIA] You can be king!
--[ZHENG gasps]

375
00:19:48,083 --> 00:19:51,583
[ZI XIA] I'll make sure
of it. I promise.

376
00:19:51,666 --> 00:19:55,583
If you have no pain,
I will just feel it for you!

377
00:19:55,666 --> 00:19:58,916
Flavors, smells, all of it!

378
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:02,375
But, it's all right.

379
00:20:02,458 --> 00:20:05,875
I really think
you can feel just fine.

380
00:20:05,958 --> 00:20:08,500
That night, weren't we
both sitting there

381
00:20:08,583 --> 00:20:11,708
moved by the moon's pure glow?

382
00:20:11,791 --> 00:20:14,916
It's all right.
I'm with you now.

383
00:20:15,000 --> 00:20:17,083
We'll go back to Qin together.

384
00:20:17,166 --> 00:20:20,875
[ZHENG inhales deeply]

385
00:20:20,958 --> 00:20:22,416
[MERCHANT 208B]
This is ridiculous!

386
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:24,416
[MERCHANT 208C]
I've got negotiating to do!

387
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:26,541
[MERCHANT 208D] The gate's
closed? Since when?

388
00:20:26,625 --> 00:20:28,250
[MERCHANT 208E]
Who's responsible for this?

389
00:20:28,333 --> 00:20:29,416
[MERCHANT 208F]
It's the Yellow Pennant!

390
00:20:29,500 --> 00:20:30,791
Those are the king's horses!

391
00:20:30,875 --> 00:20:32,000
[MERCHANT 208G]
What?

392
00:20:32,083 --> 00:20:33,166
[ZHAO HORSEMAN 208A]
Who's in charge here?

393
00:20:33,250 --> 00:20:35,708
Show yourself! Now!

394
00:20:35,791 --> 00:20:38,125
[CIVIL SERVANT 208C] It is I.
What is this concerning?

395
00:20:38,208 --> 00:20:41,208
Did a merchant named
Zi Xia pass through here?

396
00:20:41,291 --> 00:20:43,791
Yes, about twelve hours ago.

397
00:20:43,875 --> 00:20:46,166
[ZHAO HORSEMAN 208A]
Open the gate at once!

398
00:20:48,125 --> 00:20:49,250
[MERCHANT 208H]
The cavalry!

399
00:20:49,333 --> 00:20:50,625
[MERCHANT 208I]
Wow!

400
00:20:50,708 --> 00:20:52,708
[MERCHANT 208J] Is there
a battle on the way?

401
00:20:52,791 --> 00:20:54,416
[CIVIL SERVANT 208C]
That Zi Xia.

402
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:56,625
What's she done now?

403
00:21:00,625 --> 00:21:02,458
[ZI XIA]
Come.

404
00:21:02,541 --> 00:21:04,583
[ZHENG] Uuh.

405
00:21:04,666 --> 00:21:06,500
[groans]

406
00:21:06,583 --> 00:21:07,708
Lord Zheng!

407
00:21:07,791 --> 00:21:10,375
Tell me, are you all right?

408
00:21:10,458 --> 00:21:12,125
[HALLUCINATION]
What's with her?

409
00:21:12,208 --> 00:21:14,333
Zheng's not going back.

410
00:21:14,416 --> 00:21:16,416
Zheng's not going back.

411
00:21:16,500 --> 00:21:18,250
What's with her?

412
00:21:18,333 --> 00:21:20,583
You can't have him.

413
00:21:20,666 --> 00:21:23,333
We'll take him away.

414
00:21:23,416 --> 00:21:26,833
To the depths
of the earth with us.

415
00:21:26,916 --> 00:21:29,333
Don't meddle, woman.

416
00:21:29,416 --> 00:21:31,791
Or we'll take you, too.

417
00:21:31,875 --> 00:21:34,750
Take you to
the depths of the earth.

418
00:21:34,833 --> 00:21:36,958
Get away from me!
The ghosts who possess me

419
00:21:37,041 --> 00:21:39,041
are after you, Zi Xia!

420
00:21:39,125 --> 00:21:40,583
Ghosts, you say?

421
00:21:40,666 --> 00:21:42,250
[gasps]

422
00:21:47,041 --> 00:21:55,208
[GHOSTS moaning]

423
00:21:55,291 --> 00:21:57,208
[ZI XIA quavered breathing]

424
00:21:57,291 --> 00:22:00,083
[HALLUCINATION laughs]

425
00:22:01,250 --> 00:22:03,833
[ZHENG]
It's no use, Zi Xia.

426
00:22:03,916 --> 00:22:08,125
There is--there is no
escaping them now.

427
00:22:08,208 --> 00:22:09,458
[ZI XIA grunts]

428
00:22:09,541 --> 00:22:18,333
[GHOSTS moaning]

429
00:22:18,416 --> 00:22:19,875
Pull yourself together!

430
00:22:19,958 --> 00:22:21,458
There's no such
thing as ghosts!

431
00:22:21,541 --> 00:22:22,916
None of that is real!

432
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:25,416
There's no one here
with you but me!

433
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:28,041
Those are all just illusions!

434
00:22:28,125 --> 00:22:31,875
[HALLUCINATION screams]

435
00:22:33,458 --> 00:22:37,041
[GHOSTS moan]

436
00:22:37,958 --> 00:22:47,958
♪

437
00:22:48,041 --> 00:22:58,416
♪

438
00:22:58,500 --> 00:23:00,291
--[ZI XIA sighs]
--[ZHENG] Mmnn.

439
00:23:03,125 --> 00:23:05,333
[ZHENG] So warm.

440
00:23:05,416 --> 00:23:06,791
That's right.

441
00:23:06,875 --> 00:23:10,416
This is new.
This warmth here.

442
00:23:10,500 --> 00:23:15,500
It's the first time
I've ever had anyone...

443
00:23:15,583 --> 00:23:17,625
...hold me like this.

